@NODE intro "Introduction"

  @{b}Introduction@{ub}

  'DOpus 4 Plus' is a collection of useful ARexx scripts and tools for the
  legendary file manager 'Directory Opus 4'. They invent new functions or
  integrate DirOpus with other applications.

  We rewrote many older scripts that we found on our disks (removed bugs,
  optimized them), so this is probably the most complete collection of
  ARexx scripts for DirOpus.

  A note to DirOpus 5/Magellan users: Sorry, but this package is
  absolutely useless for you. The ARexx message port of DirOpus 4 differs
  quite much from that of the following versions, so the scripts in this
  collection won't work with your software...

  If you've got further requests or suggestions, don't hesitate to contact
  us (see @{" Authors " link auth}).

@ENDNODE

